    public class OnScheduleMultiHandlerManager
extends MultiHandlerManager<Function<Runnable,Runnable>>
implements Function<Runnable,Runnable>, BiConsumer<Runnable[],Function<Runnable,Runnable>>
    Handles the OnSchedule hooks.

    Use enable() to install the single global RxJavaPlugins handler.
